clsflib -- Python library to interact with the CLSF FC300
=========================================================


Installing from PyPI
--------------------

This is what you want if you just want to use clsflib:

   pip install clsflib


As a source package
-------------------
This is what you want if you are developing clsflib or want 
to make local changes to the source code.

   pip install -e <path>




See docs/ folder for documentation.
